Verification.description: For help verifying your Roblox account or your Discord account.

Challenge.description: To challenge a play or call in-game. Not for challenging anything outside an active game.

Referee.description: To report a player for something that is against league rules or our policies. Should not be used for moderation issues.

Franchise.description: For any issues regarding a team or its ownership. Requesting a gametime force, disbanding, or other ownership related questions should be done here.

Moderation.description: For any issues occurring in our Discord server. Not for any franchise/in-game issues.

Statistics.description: For any inquiries or issues about stats or stats submission. Do not make a ticket to ask when we are going to enter your stats unless it has been 48+ hours.

History.description: Report any issues with the league's history channel. Could be incorrect information, or just a question about something.

Paid Promotions.description: To purchase a paid promotion or offer a partnership. Price will depend on which league you are requesting for. For unpaid partnerships, your server must be of similar size to ours.
